OL,3,CScottish Government scraps plans for
OL,4,Cnew national park
OL,6,FHow did we get here? Our report looks
OL,7,Finto the history of the plans to bring
OL,8,Fa new national park to Galloway.
OL,10,FThe Scottish Government has announced
OL,11,Fthat its plans for a new national park
OL,12,Fin Galloway and Ayrshire have been
OL,13,Fscrapped.
OL,15,FSpeaking in Holyrood this afternoon
OL,16,F(29 May, 2025), Rural Affairs
OL,17,FSecretary Mairi Gougeon MSP said the
OL,18,Fgovernment had "made the decision not
OL,19,Fto proceed with the designation of a
OL,20,Fnew national park for Galloway and
OL,21,FAyrshire".
