OL,6,FShe said the government had "weighed
OL,7,Fup the arguments for and against" the
OL,8,Fproposal, adding that the public
OL,9,Fconsultation had seen 54% of
OL,10,Frespondents outline their opposition,
OL,11,Fwhile 42% were in favour.
OL,13,FThe majority of consultation responses
OL,14,Fwere completed by people living and
OL,15,Fworking in Galloway and Ayrshire.
OL,17,FTaking account of local responses
OL,18,Falone, 57% opposed the proposal while
OL,19,F40% were supportive.
