OL,7,Fgreatest among environment, recreation
OL,8,Fand tourism sectors, whilst
OL,9,Flandowners, land managers and those
OL,10,Fworking in the farming, forestry and
OL,11,Frenewable energy sectors had the
OL,12,Fstrongest reservations.
