OL,6,F"Based on the evidence gathered during
OL,7,Fthe investigation and consultation,
OL,8,Fthe reporter has advised that, whilst
OL,9,Fit considers that the proposed area
OL,10,Fmeets the conditions for a national
OL,11,Fpark set out in the legislation, the
OL,12,Fproposal does not have sufficient
OL,13,Fclarity, nor has it garnered
OL,14,Fsufficient local support to proceed to
OL,15,Fthe next stage of designation.
