OL,3,CScottish Government scraps plans for
OL,4,Cnew national park
OL,6,F"We have weighed up the arguments for
OL,7,Fand against the creation of a new
OL,8,Fnational park in the area, taking full
OL,9,Faccount of the potential economic,
OL,10,Fsocial and environmental factors, and
OL,11,Fwe have come to the conclusion not to
OL,12,Fproceed with the designation of a
OL,13,Fnational park in Galloway and
OL,14,FAyrshire."
OL,16,FThe Scottish Government had committed
OL,17,Fto designating at least one new
OL,18,Fnational park in Scotland by 2026.
OL,20,FGalloway was selected as the preferred
OL,21,Foption in July last year.
