OL,6,FSince then, the proposal has become
OL,7,Fhighly controversial, with a campaign
OL,8,Fgroup opposing the plans attracting
OL,9,Fhundreds of followers on social media
OL,10,Fand protests held across the region.
OL,12,FNatureScot held a public consultation
OL,13,Fon the plans, which concluded in
OL,14,FFebruary, with the results then handed
OL,15,Fover to the Scottish Government for a
OL,16,Fdecision.
OL,18,FThe results of the consultation have
OL,19,Fyet to be announced publicly.
