OL,3,CScottish Government scraps plans for
OL,4,Cnew national park
OL,6,FSupporters of the park say it would
OL,7,Fbring an economic boost to the area,
OL,8,Fattracting visitors and putting
OL,9,FGalloway on the map.
OL,11,FThose against the proposals said it
OL,12,Fwould drive up house prices, put a
OL,13,Fstrain on local infrastructure and
OL,14,Fthat it would bring unnecessary
OL,15,Fbureaucracy and complexity for farmers.
OL,17,FIn February, Dumfries and Galloway
OL,18,FCouncil said it was 'undecided' on
OL,19,Fwhether the plans should go ahead.
